Package com.landawn.abacus.util

Record Class Sheet.Cell<R,C,V>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.landawn.abacus.util.Sheet.Cell<R,C,V>
Type Parameters:
R - the type of the row keys
C - the type of the column keys
V - the type of the values stored in the cells
Record Components:
rowKey - the key of the row
columnKey - the key of the column
value - the value stored in the cell
Enclosing class:
Sheet<R,C,V>
public static record Sheet.Cell<R,C,V>(R rowKey, C columnKey, V value) extends Record
A record representing a cell in the Sheet. A cell is identified by a row key of type R, a column key of type C, and contains a value of type V.
